=============================================================

This is a README file to Ganglia integration of the Monitoring module of the CHOReOS project

=============================================================





=============================================================

HOW TO COMPILE:

1) Install requirements: maven 3.x, jdk1.6, eclipse IDE
	
	
2) Clone source repository. To do this run the comands below:

	git clone git://github.com/felps/CHOReOS-Monitoring-Service.git
	cd CHOReOS-Monitoring-Service/ChoreosMonitoring
	mvn install

	cd ../glimpse/
	mvn eclipse:eclipse
	
3) Open your eclipse IDE and import both projects:
	
	File->Export->Generals->Existing projects into workspace->select a root directory->(put path to workspace)
	click in Glimpse project and import it
	click in ChoreosMonitoring and import it
	
4) Export to jar file:

	To do this, right click on Glimpse project and click on export menu. 
	Select Java->Runnable jar file and press Next button. Select Launcher 
	configuration to GlimpseProbeLauncher - Glimpse, give a  path to save 
	the genarated jar file and press finish button.

=============================================================

=============================================================

RUNNING:

	To run just enter jar directory and type the follow command
	
	java -jar <jar-file-name>.jar [link to activemq link]
	
	If link to activemq is specified, tcp://dsbchoreos.petalslink.org:61616 will be used

=============================================================